info.author: Robin Bakker
info.name: akeneo-connector
info.summary: Akeneo Connector is a Python package that simplifies interacting with Akeneo's REST API. It provides classes for making HTTP requests to Akeneo endpoints, handling pagination in responses, and managing product data in Akeneo.
